cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image matching and deep learning architecture, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of unsupervised-discriminative learning approach and fine-grained datasets also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The application of the approach to single-view reconstruction and the use of artificial data suggest the possibility of the paper belonging to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of neural networks and deep learning suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
